</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="52.[313,1268,1616,1736]" pageId="52" pageNumber="2704">
<emphasis box="[353,481,1680,1704]" italics="true" pageId="52" pageNumber="2704">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pena Cantero &amp; Vervoort" authorityYear="2003" box="[718,817,1680,1704]" class="Hydrozoa" family="Sertulariidae" genus="Staurotheca" kingdom="Animalia" order="Leptothecata" pageId="52" pageNumber="2704" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="profunda">
<emphasis box="[718,817,1680,1704]" italics="true" pageId="52" pageNumber="2704">profunda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
refers to the deep waters from which it originates.
</paragraph>
